  "title": "Eq. 10 -> Eq. 11",
  "intro": [
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "value": "The point of this reduction is to turn Eq. 10 from a mixed locked-and-drifting expression into one real self-consistency relation for the synchronized part of the population."
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "value": "Once it is in Eq. 11 form, the next move is simple: divide by the nonzero order parameter and expose the onset condition used in the following transformation."
    }
  ],
